# Rss Tecnology

## To access the project

```
To access the project, simply clone the repository
use the command: git clone
```

## To run the project
```
To run the project, install the following tools.
1- MySQL Workbench
2- Xamp
```
## To execute
```
To execute
use the npm start command
```
